{"tid":153544,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【評測】Netgear AirCard 810S","createTime":"2017-03-12T16:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T16:02:42.000Z","uid":4055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06affc66cc92b725e3ceeef6fb4cb0ae586c1508","tid":153544,"uid":4055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.enterpr1se.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/netgear-aircard-810s-01-640x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enterpr1se.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fnetgear-aircard-810s-01-640x480.jpg&h=d2a05cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次測試 790 時，810 剛剛推出<br />\n依家部機其實都出咗半年，可能唔少師兄都用緊，但係我依家先借到嚟試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有得試總好過無得試嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但今次問代理借到嘅只係美版嘅 810S，而唔係歐版<br />\n上網睇過佢未必支援香港嘅 3CA，可能都係用得 2CA，不過就一定用得到，對於常去美國同台灣嘅人會啱用啲<br />\n今次測試剛剛好撞正 CSL 搞果個「競速測試」，所以就去到佢門口試，最高試到 164Mbps<br />\n但平時係其他地方測速就及唔上自己部華為 e5786<br />\n我估係可能入面嘅 setting 同香港 network 唔係咁甲，始終係美版<br />\n不過點都好，都可以當做參考嘅<br />\n<br />\n測試全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.enterpr1se.info/2017/03/netgear-810s-review/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enterpr1se.info%2F2017%2F03%2Fnetgear-810s-review%2F&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e6128f56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.enterpr1se.info/2017/03/netgear-810s-review/</a>"}]}